        public void sort(int[] array)
        Realization of sorting array via Merge Sort algorithm, where initial array is subdivided into two parts, each of which is sorted with BubbleSortDown.sort(int[]). The parts are further merged with MergeSorter.mergeArrays(int[], int[], int, int, int[]) method from MergeSorter.

        sort in class AbstractSorter
        Parameters:
